description: This Chainlink VRF common Plezier purrs with a rating of 17, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 34, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 2 for North, 2 for East, Nine Lives for South, and Box for West. Plezier has the personality suit of yenta. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/70172-22944-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Plezier [34 Votes, Common]
